HEADWORD: Inobservant
<hw>In`ob*serv"ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inobservans</ets>. See <er>In-</er> not, and
<er>Observant</er>.]</ety> <def>Not observant; regardless;
